  },
  {
    "row": 3,
    "rowsha": "xaZSsScwcAUQt8pNnBRZ9r/Jyj0OR/GKaAYbGBLO6JI=",
    "originContent": "improved [radiko.jp](https://radiko.jp) extractor plugin for yt-dlp (fast and areafree)",
    "translatedContent": "향상된 [radiko.jp](https://radiko.jp) 추출기 플러그인 for yt-dlp (빠르고 지역 제한 없음)"
  },
  {
    "row": 4,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 5,
    "rowsha": "ezebnvEXL2o+n5M6sBwU8Tu69VKpW8wakwPaoDax5Vw=",
    "originContent": "<p>yt-dlp-rajiko lets you download Japanese radio shows from <a href=\"https://radiko.jp\">radiko.jp</a> without a VPN, using <a href=\"https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp\">yt-dlp</a>.",
    "translatedContent": "<p>yt-dlp-rajiko를 사용하면 <a href=\"https://radiko.jp\">radiko.jp</a>에서 VPN 없이 일본 라디오 방송을 다운로드할 수 있습니다. <a href=\"https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp\">yt-dlp</a>를 사용합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 6,
    "rowsha": "hCfu3W49PRDMzZd4jxfEMPObHMnGtynjKLlD55UHQSs=",
    "originContent": "It downloads quickly, and works for any participating station*, from anywhere in the world.<br>",
    "translatedContent": "빠르게 다운로드하며 전 세계 어디서나 참여하는 모든 방송국*에서 작동합니다.<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "Nb4JIk7wtYlVuRJD9s+/OIvbvvAfbbsGdNkS4on/0Jg=",
    "originContent": "<small>*except NHK, but they have <a href=\"https://www.nhk.or.jp/radio/\">their own site</a> which is supported",
    "translatedContent": "<small>*NHK 제외, 그러나 NHK는 <a href=\"https://www.nhk.or.jp/radio/\">자체 사이트</a>가 있으며 yt-dlp 자체에서 지원됩니다</small></p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "APhIH04MA1p8t8aedQf1/H6d04w/L+trvKESpkyGA0M=",
    "originContent": "in yt-dlp proper</small></p>",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "<p>개인 저장용으로 의도되었으며 상업적 용도가 아닙니다. 가능하다면 radiko Premium에 가입해 주세요.<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "<small>(무료 소프트웨어이므로, 강제 사항이 아니라 저의 정중한 부탁입니다. radiko가 계속 존재할 수 있도록 꼭 해주세요)<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "+L7hFxnMyWo3lwHa/UATgCbQpFQHezrML7eS7Hw/f/k=",
    "originContent": "<p>Intended for personal archiving, not for commercial use. Please subscribe to radiko Premium if you are able.<br>",
    "translatedContent": "(또한, timefree30 플랜을 사용하면 yt-dlp와 함께 사용할 수 있습니다 :P)"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "GQqctken8sMEGjhoaW4ZIYdb4zu2Fpvq0wSQPZGkFsw=",
    "originContent": "<small>(It's Free Software, so this is just me asking nicely, not a hard requirement. but you should do it so that radiko can keep existing)<br>",
    "translatedContent": "</small></p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "8UNZ3ZbXlwE1PqvxsfuMGuIuXnLkkYM23KBAEfNZuog=",
    "originContent": "(also, if you get the timefree30 plan you can use it with yt-dlp :P)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "QHC77D1tfuVooaJi5UWAxtc5Z3fJezLxyNGjTcwl4Mo=",
    "originContent": "</small></p>",
    "translatedContent": "### [日本語  🇯🇵](https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/index.ja.html)"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "A/ZLljsE3WGXLapnV7VteottVtpNPJrqjTTpqMcWRqo=",
    "originContent": "### [日本語  🇯🇵](https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/index.ja.html)",
    "translatedContent": "## 설치"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "oV0SUDvwD2VN8Gi9nlr2JZ2xcDrASmE2W5kc5SVX5eo=",
    "originContent": "## Installation",
    "translatedContent": "[플러그인 번들 다운로드](https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/dl/yt_dlp_rajiko-latest.bundle.zip) 또는 `pip install yt-dlp-rajiko`"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "x0/OS5jLsbS1kXm2rxoZneporLCM9hns/jEgw/bG8BM=",
    "originContent": "[Download the plugin bundle](https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/dl/yt_dlp_rajiko-latest.bundle.zip) or `pip install yt-dlp-rajiko`",
    "translatedContent": "<p>yt-dlp 2025.02.19 이상 버전이 필요합니다.</p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "3owQimPChTUSbg9tGpskxJwWa2fNXPrJH3v38GhSYZQ=",
    "originContent": "<p>Requires yt-dlp 2025.02.19 or newer.</p>",
    "translatedContent": "<p>pip로 yt-dlp를 설치했다면 위의 pip 명령어를 사용하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "만약 <code>pipx</code>로 설치했다면,"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "ZkXBi10d+rwPQS1SH8D0zpoiUrEmkO0Ay+1to79HWDc=",
    "originContent": "<p>If you installed yt-dlp with pip, use the pip command above.",
    "translatedContent": "<code>pipx inject yt-dlp yt-dlp-rajiko</code>를 사용하여 yt-dlp 환경에 플러그인을 설치하세요.</p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "yqQxHlP2QDhcIMTlQ7clqzsYsJtZp9pGDSIswmJJ4II=",
    "originContent": "If you installed yt-dlp with <code>pipx</code>,",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "iWZSguyWjBO/kZBcGvuHw783V5cVS/nAD1+7FbnlMCk=",
    "originContent": "use <code>pipx inject yt-dlp yt-dlp-rajiko</code> to install the plugin in yt-dlp's environment.</p>",
    "translatedContent": "<p>.exe/바이너리 또는 다른 방법으로 설치했다면,"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "번들을 다운로드하여 아래 위치 중 하나에 넣으세요: </p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "HL93+VPJxDMHdtMBVI33l5SRErq7jeRzxn9DSpYwydQ=",
    "originContent": "<p>If you installed with the .exe/binary or any other method,",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "aWUyfCneLBNG2PHK5T44VGvXy90GqMo8ConBqxSwiNI=",
    "originContent": "download the bundle and place it in one of these locations: </p>",
    "translatedContent": "<ul>"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "\t<li><code>%appdata%\\yt-dlp\\plugins\\</code> (Windows에서)</li>"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "OYhBHnFsMsICEifoxTioM0B16t+CrEUsSHiWn/2NIkQ=",
    "originContent": "<ul>",
    "translatedContent": "\t<li><code>~/.config/yt-dlp/plugins/</code> (Linux 및 Mac에서)</li>"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "Z0Ov0xPKm4eFxe5CcEPbCG65IgXfUrF0pDc+/xgEQnY=",
    "originContent": "\t<li><code>%appdata%\\yt-dlp\\plugins\\</code> (on Windows)</li>",
    "translatedContent": "\t<li><code>yt-dlp.exe</code> 옆에 <code>yt-dlp-plugins</code> 폴더 생성 <a href=\"https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/i/installation-pluginsfolder2.png\">(이와 같이)</a><br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "PGP9B39XD+Tb/XCT5Dn7o7O9Qy9m/krSFzHmML54/Rg=",
    "originContent": "\t<li><code>~/.config/yt-dlp/plugins/</code> (on Linux and Mac)</li>",
    "translatedContent": "\t<li><a href=\"https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp#installing-plugins\">yt-dlp 문서</a>에 나열된 다른 위치</li>"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "uYxAstgaGN7wsOFlwV8Smf3Nf01AP1s+VuRHHGg4TYw=",
    "originContent": "\t<li>a <code>yt-dlp-plugins</code> folder next to your <code>yt-dlp.exe</code> <a href=\"https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/i/installation-pluginsfolder2.png\">(like this)</a><br>",
    "translatedContent": "</ul>"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "DieSPrgY3TDZTY0X5PUn+U5sc3NbQYHD7uX72RmjeGo=",
    "originContent": "\t<li>anywhere else listed in <a href=\"https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp#installing-plugins\">the yt-dlp documentation</a>.</li>",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "NIhF2IBLXIleKik4Qj7Rey3EzTqtn5ZsE+DtiSI7L5A=",
    "originContent": "</ul>",
    "translatedContent": "<p>해당 폴더가 없으면 직접 만들어야 합니다.<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "<b>zip 파일을 압축 해제할 필요가 없습니다.</b></p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "3z94sjk3wKfEV+o5lWS6gMDpsuaVobvd3vLINRSWQlE=",
    "originContent": "<p>You'll have to create those folders if they don't already exist.<br>",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "Lzmu/VEFWWUEhJgRrYIB8ngAmb5SQTyrm2WjvwrW6iI=",
    "originContent": "<b>There is no need to extract the zip file.</b></p>",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "YzPBgBMSAYf+G+ab8Ee2L0Ls+MTUt/7PpVc5HIVgY5o=",
    "originContent": "<p>You can check you've installed correctly by running <code>yt-dlp -v</code> and looking for the <code>[debug] Extractor Plugins:</code> or <code>[debug] Plugin directories:</code> lines. <a href=\"https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/i/plugincheck.png\">(like this)</a>",
    "translatedContent": "<p>설치가 제대로 되었는지 확인하려면 <code>yt-dlp -v</code>를 실행하고 <code>[debug] Extractor Plugins:</code> 또는 <code>[debug] Plugin directories:</code> 줄을 찾으세요. <a href=\"https://427738.xyz/yt-dlp-rajiko/i/plugincheck.png\">(이와 같이)</a>"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "dSdvPNAZSmR86FDDSF6tkQUCVfI9qmACHOR5tThOetY=",
    "originContent": "</p>",
    "translatedContent": "</p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "Gq6ZYUd4uQvEoo+xpBW2JOIZCg4gx42EIc6XkBETM8s=",
    "originContent": "More information about yt-dlp plugins is available from [yt-dlp's documentation](https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp#plugins).",
    "translatedContent": "yt-dlp 플러그인에 대한 자세한 정보는 [yt-dlp 문서](https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp#plugins)에서 확인할 수 있습니다."
  },
  {
